Class AuthRequiredParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.AuthRequiredParams

  • public final class AuthRequiredParams
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents parameters that are passed to the NetworkDelegate.onAuthRequired(AuthRequiredParams) method.
    表示传递给NetworkDelegate.onAuthRequired（AuthRequiredParams）方法的参数。
